{
  "texts": [
    "Figure 3 illustrates the specific implementation process between these two tasks.",
    "The process begins with an input text that embedded with positional, segment, and token embeddings based on SciBERT.",
    "These embeddings are then processed through multiple transformer layers to capture contextual information from the input text.",
    "The output from the transformer layers was fed into a Softmax function to assign a function label to each input text.",
    "At this point, we can automatically obtain the chapter structure information for each paper."
  ]
}